    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《浪客诺特》是一款轻度肉鸽动作游戏，背景设定在一座陷入宇宙混乱的巨型空间站。空间站正逐步滑向失控的深渊，曾经的人类居民已被扭曲成不可名状的恐怖存在。而你，作为不幸的勇士，必须直面魂类战斗的洗礼，在暴力肆虐的空间站回廊中存活下来，方有资格揭开这场灾变的真相。​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032830/extras/8469ffd6a99b9f420a34831b8d299010.poster.avif?t=1768633849\" width=800 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032830/extras/8469ffd6a99b9f420a34831b8d299010.webm?t=1768633849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032830/extras/8469ffd6a99b9f420a34831b8d299010.mp4?t=1768633849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将会扮演浪客诺特，登上这座曾经充满活力的空间站……或者说，探索仅剩的断壁残垣。越是深入空间站深处，周遭环境便愈发阴森诡谲，而遭遇的敌人，也越来越不像人类。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032830/extras/785d59258b1994a4e4c8142228d77250.poster.avif?t=1768633849\" width=800 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032830/extras/785d59258b1994a4e4c8142228d77250.webm?t=1768633849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032830/extras/785d59258b1994a4e4c8142228d77250.mp4?t=1768633849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >借助先进的时间操控技术，即使你的生命体征消失，也可起死回生。在这个人类能够按需下载新技能的未来，空间站各处散落着逝者的记忆碎片。每块碎片都有可能蕴藏着失传的技能或天赋，只待有人来解锁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032830/extras/99c2c7aceb60229b50a45151694db7ac.poster.avif?t=1768633849\" width=800 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032830/extras/99c2c7aceb60229b50a45151694db7ac.webm?t=1768633849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032830/extras/99c2c7aceb60229b50a45151694db7ac.mp4?t=1768633849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次冒险都会带来全新的挑战，供你探索瞬息万变的路径，并与成群敌人展开激战。每当乘坐空间站电梯深入一层，你都可以收集到更多的记忆碎片，探索更多游戏内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032830/extras/d733e5f87115fd36f80bc37d3c16e52d.poster.avif?t=1768633849\" width=800 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032830/extras/d733e5f87115fd36f80bc37d3c16e52d.webm?t=1768633849\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032830/extras/d733e5f87115fd36f80bc37d3c16e52d.mp4?t=1768633849\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >刀刃的铮鸣回荡于空间站空荡摇曳的走廊间，每个转角都似有惊变潜伏……无论你是追求刀刀入肉的搏杀艺术，还是钟情于远程终结的致命优雅，这场清理任务都会让你永生难忘。</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 日语, 韩语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 简体中文, 繁体中文, 土耳其语, 乌克兰语",
